Dialogue: 1,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, kids?
