Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁住在深海的大菠萝里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who lives in a pineapple under the sea?
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.91,0:00:15.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方方黄黄伸缩自如
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Absorbent and yellow and porous is he
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果四处探险是你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If nautical nonsense be something you wish
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:00:23.67,0:00:26.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就敲敲甲板让大鱼开路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:26.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then drop on the deck and flop like a fish
