Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊  大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:00:59.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah, the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么迷人  那么美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so fascinating, so wonderful
