Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这我们能看到裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we see Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充满着生机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:06.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,teeming with life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住着我最喜欢的生物之一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,home of one of my favorite creatures
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他当然住在菠萝里  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:13.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course he lives in a pineapple, you silly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是个重要日子  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's the big day, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308.143,923.333)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:34.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.69,0:01:37.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没穿衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.69,0:01:37.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm naked
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要为今天保持身体最佳状态  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Got to be in top physical condition for today, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(308.143,923.333)}小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:54.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900.417,190)}我爱痛苦
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
