Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:16.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:23.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有史以来最棒的提供饮食的餐厅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The finest eating establishment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:26.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever established for eating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:30.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(478.889,502)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王  蟹黄堡之家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab, home of the Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(721.668,790)}招聘
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,窗户上还贴着招聘广告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:33.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a help wanted sign in the window
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我多年以来都在梦想着这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For years, I've been dreaming of this moment
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要直接进去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go in there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一路正步走到经理面前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,march straight to the manager
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直视他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look him straight in the eye
Dialogue: 1,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他撂狠话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lay it on the line
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I can't do this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.93,0:02:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.10,0:02:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, you're not
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要去蟹堡王  拿到那份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:51.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to The Krusty Krab and get that job
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到  看不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't, don't you see?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还不够好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:55.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not good enough
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁出生后的第一句话是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whose first words were
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能为你点餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"May I take your order?"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.82,0:02:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mine were
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁在木工工厂里用牙签做出了锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who made a spatula out of toothpicks in wood shop?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.08,0:03:04.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:04.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:06.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是黄色带洞的大方块
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a big-yellow cube with holes?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
