Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:26.68,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1207.226,208.667)}失败者
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, SpongeBob
