Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他会想要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could he possibly want?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.73,0:03:31.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.73,0:03:31.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝加油  祝自己加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go, SpongeBob, go, self
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:36.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1095.174,656.667)}招聘
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:39.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before it's too late
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.15,0:03:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to tell you about--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,申请上船  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Permission to come aboard, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一生都在自我训练只为了这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been training my whole life for the day
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能够加入蟹堡王团队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can join the Krusty crew
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:46.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  什么时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, uh, when do I start?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.76,0:04:11.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  看来你很容易晕船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:08.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, lad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:11.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it looks like you don't even have your sea legs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, please
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会证明我是个当厨师的好材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll prove I'm fry cook material
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去问章鱼哥  他会替我担保的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ask Squidward, he'll vouch for me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子  给你一个测试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, lad, we'll give you a test
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你通过了就可以加入蟹堡王团队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and if you pass you'll be on the Krusty crew
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出去给我找一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go out and fetch me a--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a--
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水动力锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hydrodynamic spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.58,0:04:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带左右铲配件和涡轮发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with port and starboard attachments and turbo drive
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找不到就别回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't come back till you get one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一把水动力锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One hydrodynamic spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带左右铲配件  涡轮发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with port and starboard attachments, turbo drive
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就来  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming right up, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Carry on
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们再也见不着那旱鸭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll never see that lubber again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水动力什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A hydro what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670.978,539.333)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家都注意点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乘客请在座位上坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Passengers are to stay seated
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请勿将鳍伸出窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and not put your fins out the windows
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听起来像舱门打开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounded like hatch doors
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你闻到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you smell it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那味道  某种难闻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:25.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That smell, a kind of smelly smell
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.34,0:05:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这难闻的味道  味道又很难闻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A smelly smell that smells smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchovies
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凤尾鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anchovies
Dialogue: 1,0:05:37.52,0:05:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(452.209,435.334)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你们  求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, please
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种行为成何体统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this any way to behave?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.28,0:05:51.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:51.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能体面一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we show a little decency
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.54,0:05:59.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整整齐齐地在收银台前面排好队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and form a neat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:59.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,single-file line in front of the register?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:06.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(566.93,155.333)}便宜货超市
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,便宜货超市  满足购铲需求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:05.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barg'N-Mart, meeting all your spatula needs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(140.065,328.667)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船上全体成员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All hands on deck
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作都快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your anchors out of your pants
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.47,0:06:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要求你们排好队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One single-file line is all I ask
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,封住舱口  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Batten down the hatches, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船进水了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're taking on water, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要妈妈  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want my mommy, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,锅铲  锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spatula, spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带左右铲的锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Port and starboard attachments
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人落水了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:33.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man overboard
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快爬啊  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Climb, Mr. Squidward, climb
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the end
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,申请上船  船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Permission to come aboard, captain
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁订购了锅铲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did someone order a spatula?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  一个水动力锅铲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, one hydrodynamic spatula
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带左右铲的配件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with port and starboard attachments
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不要忘了涡轮发动机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and let's not forget the turbo drive
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们信不信他们库存只剩一个了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would you believe they only had one in stock?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:17.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's hungry?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,困扰你的事  困扰不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Things that bother you never bother me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422.863,579.333)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我快乐无比
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:23.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm as happy as pie
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.83,0:07:25.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852.395,856.667)}肉饼
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活在阳光下  爱在月光里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Living in the sunlight, loving in the moonlight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光常在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Having a wonderful time
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽然钱不多  但需求不大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Haven't got a lot, I don't need a lot
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咖啡一毛就够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coffee's only a dime
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活在阳光下  爱在月光里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:36.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Living in the sunlight, loving in the moonlight
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光常在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.06,0:07:37.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Having a wonderful time
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,相信我的话  我的这一生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just take it from me, I'm just as
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十分无忧无虑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,free as any daughter
Dialogue: 1,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿想随时  愿意想如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do what I like just when I
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做我喜欢的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like and how I love it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当我入晚年  愿长留于此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm right here to stay, when I'm old and gray
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巅峰永久不退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be right in my prime
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活在阳光下  爱在月光里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:08:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Living in the sunlight, loving in the moonlight
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光常在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Having a wonderful time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最强的快餐经营技能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was the finest fast-foodsmanship I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎加入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome aboard
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:21.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(828.384,630)}海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可  可是蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, but Mr. Krabs--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为海绵宝宝欢呼三声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hip, hip--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.19,0:08:26.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:26.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hip, hip--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.19,0:08:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hip, hip--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:29.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.15,0:08:29.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:29.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs--
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要到我的岗位清点战利品了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be in my quarters counting up the booty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  蟹堡王的员工们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Krusty crew
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要点什么  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would you like to order, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来一份蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One Krabby Patty, please
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:09:02.27,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(449.542,467.333)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:50.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.67,0:08:55.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  看看你新招的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:55.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, come see your new employee
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美好时光常在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:57.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Having a wonderful time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.85,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(358,307)}鼓风机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正姚体\bord0\shad5\pos(719,1062)\fad(112,0)}你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1092.506,408.667)}吹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(852.395,758)}吸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:57.90,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(151,143)}橡树屋的茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz11.21\pos(262.788,296.667)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:00.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz11.21\pos(286.799,678)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:02.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:02.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.82\pos(420.195,264.667)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.05\pos(278.796,296.666)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz14.05\pos(390.848,656.666)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四个触手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four stingers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前在哪见过这位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where have I seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(847.059,560.667)}实地导览
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了  陆地松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is, Land Squirrel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1052.488,774)}陆地松鼠
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只小松鼠有麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That little squirrel is in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招  你这低等蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:03.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that, you sorry old clam
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你需要学会礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You need to learn some manners
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的样子马上就要难看得不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're about as ugly as homemade soup
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁  陆地松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray, Land Squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:16.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住  小松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, little squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打得很有两下子  巨大蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have fought well, giant clam
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好被打败吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare to be vanquished
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我弄得开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:36.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm actually doing it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的壳归我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your shell is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住  小方块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:13:58.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on there, little square dude
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也喜欢空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You like karate, too
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么  你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what's your name?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.75,0:14:25.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么称呼你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:25.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So, what do you call yourself?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.71,0:14:29.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:29.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.60,0:14:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你可要瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, SpongeBob, take a gander at this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:52.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:53.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:15:00.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们之间的关系会紧密得不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we could be tighter than bark on a tree
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like you too, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你头上戴的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is that on your head?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是空气头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my air helmet
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能试戴一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:15.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May I try it on?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不行  我还要用它来呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heck no, I need it to breathe
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须要空气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to have my air
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爱空气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love air
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Air is good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气是我的特色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, air is my middle name
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气越多就越好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The more air, the better
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't get enough air
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那明天到我家来点茶和饼干怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about coming over tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.61,0:15:32.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for tea and cookies then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(996.462,203.333)}珊迪的树屋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:34.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729.672,998)}你在这里
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be late
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:40.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's air?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚碰见了这个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just met this girl
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她戴着顶装满空气的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She wears a hat full of air
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是说她摆架子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you mean she "puts on airs"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(916.426,920)}穿着空气
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.97,0:15:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess so
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那都是花俏话术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's just fancy talk
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.06,0:16:01.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你想要花俏  就这样伸出小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:16:01.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want to be fancy hold your pinky up like this
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,伸得越高  你就越花俏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The higher you hold it, the fancier you are
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.61,0:16:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再高点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Higher
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.52,0:16:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样才叫花俏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's fancy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们就该叫你花俏宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They should call you SpongeBob FancyPants
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,犹豫不决  就伸小指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When in doubt, pinky out
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:20.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在外面看你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be watching
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.09,0:16:28.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.09,0:16:28.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.71,0:16:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就让你进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:32.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll let you in
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  事情非常不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, something's gone terribly wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本没有水在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:04.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no water in--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.92,0:17:08.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:08.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然没有水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Course there's no water
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有空气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing but air
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.10,0:17:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No water?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这压根不成问题  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ain't a problem, is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Problem?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对空气就是这个看法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's how I like my air
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With no water
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做了德克萨斯茶和饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made Texas tea and cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, come on in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可不算进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's not in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这小家伙可真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a funny little dude
Dialogue: 1,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  我来带你参观
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll give you the grand tour
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.39,0:18:01.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我的私人空气罩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:01.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So this is my own private little air bubble
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里的空气是最干燥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:04.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This air is the driest--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最纯净
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:06.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Purest--
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最空气的空气  全海洋无可匹敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Most airiest air in the whole sea
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边是我的小鸟洗澡池
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:12.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over there is my birdbath
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那棵是我的橡树
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's my oak tree
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给我提供更多空气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It provides me with extra air
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这座穹顶是用强度最高的聚氨酯做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This dome is made of the strongest polyurethane
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所谓聚氨酯是塑料的高级说法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a fancy name for plastic
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:26.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't that just the bee's knees?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧  运到这也不算容易事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell you what, weren't easy getting here neither
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先  我得把它抬到一艘大船上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First, I had to hitch it up to a big ol' boat
Dialogue: 1,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的跑步机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's my treadmill
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就靠那个保持最佳身材
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's how I stay in tiptop shape
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's have that tea now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小指  小指
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinky, pinky
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给你带了一点鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I brought you some flowers
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.62,0:19:04.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.62,0:19:04.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.09,0:19:13.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:13.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:17.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm okay
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可是来这参观的第一个海洋生物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're the first sea critter to ever visit
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.05,0:19:24.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想象不到是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:24.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine why
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能给你提供些什么东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get you anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water would be nice
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把这些花插进花瓶里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to put these in a vase
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take your time
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须从这地方逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们之间的关系会紧密得不得了的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could be tighter than bark on a tree
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,犹豫不决  就伸小指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When in doubt, pinky out
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:59.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need water
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水是给懦夫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water is for quitters
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些鲜花可真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:12.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, these flowers are just beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.90,0:20:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,插进装满冰水的花瓶就能活得更久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll live much, much longer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a vase full of ice-cold water
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来自我介绍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:21.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So tell me about yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当一个海底生物肯定很迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It must be fascinating being a sea critter
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.04,0:20:29.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:29.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饼干好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's the cookies
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be right back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:45.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I definitely don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:49.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:50.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:59.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.69,0:21:03.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:03.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:04.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.86,0:21:05.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:05.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小指  小指
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:09.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinky, pinky
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a quitter
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不能临阵脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:22.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't leave now
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会搞砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll blow it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气不好  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:26.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Air is not good, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:29.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Air is not good
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这只是太害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're just being shy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你表现得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing fine
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不会让你搞砸的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let you blow
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.33,0:21:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么鬼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of place is this?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.45,0:21:57.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面根本没有水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:57.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no water in here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直想跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried to tell you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须马上出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got to get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're doing it wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, no
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.68,0:22:10.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们必须出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:10.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to get out
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.26,0:22:13.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:13.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come and get it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定会喜欢上这
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're all going to like this--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  这样应该就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:26.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There, that ought to do it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.45,0:22:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要水就早点说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you all needed water, you should have asked
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.03,0:22:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为新朋友干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I propose a toast, to new friends
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.71,0:22:41.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:41.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.59,0:22:44.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们能喜欢浓茶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:44.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope you all like your tea strong
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Drink up
